/**
 * Controls the bandwidth-floor mitigation: the reduction of the inner control loop
 * bandwidth on a structurally flexible axis — the primary oscillation stabilizer. When
 * SpaceCenter::MitigationMode::automatic (the default) it engages on a latched axis
 * while holding (and during a detected limit cycle). SpaceCenter::MitigationMode::off
 * never reduces the bandwidth; SpaceCenter::MitigationMode::forced keeps it fully
 * reduced at all times.
 */
